<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="EXAMPLES"><a class="permalink" href="#EXAMPLES">EXAMPLES</a></h1>
<div class="Bd Bd-indent"><code class="Li">mdconfig /dev/md0c 2048
  &amp;</code></div>
<p class="Pp">Configures the memory disk <span class="Pa">md0c</span> with one
    megabyte of user-space memory.</p>
</section>
